'''Mutonium''' was a very rare and valuable ore that was found in the [[Stenness Node]].

The [[Nessie]]s of the Stenness Node transported mutonium using [[Ithullan ore hauler]]s.<ref name="EGVV">''[[The Essential Guide to Vehicles and Vessels]]''</ref>

